title: Be Comfortable With Who You Are | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Be Comfortable With Who You Are | Joel Osteen
description:
Instead of comparing or competing with those around us, God wants us to appreciate the gifts and talents He's given us. If you'll use what you have to the best of your ability, His anointing will cause you to go further than you could imagine! 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
